Class Munchlax

java.lang.Object
  greenfoot.Actor

          Munchlax

public class Munchlax
extends Character

Munchax, a character. This is the player, and it runs across the map while collecting berries. The player can control the movement. Just like all other characters, munchlax has health and experience, but that influences his health for battles.
